---
// No imports needed for static image approach
---

<div class="map-container">
  <div class="next-year-teaser animate-fade-in">
    <h2 class="next-year-title">Our New Venue</h2>
    <p class="next-year-description">
      We're excited to announce that our 2026 festival will be hosted at the <span class="venue-highlight">Harris Theater</span>, with more spacious accommmodations including 190+ seats!
    </p>
    <div class="map-content">
      <div class="map-image-container">
        <img 
          src="/assets/venues/harris-theater-map.jpg" 
          alt="Map of Harris Theater location" 
          class="venue-map"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="map-info">
        <h3 class="venue-name">Harris Theater</h3>
        <p class="venue-address">809 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA 15222</p>
        <p class="venue-location">Located in the heart of downtown Pittsburgh's Cultural District</p>
        
        <div class="venue-description">
          <p>The Harris Theater is one of the most active arts facilities in the region, showing art films nearly every day of the year. Named after John P. Harris, co-founder of the Nickelodeon (the first theater dedicated solely to motion pictures), it features contemporary, foreign, and classic films.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="parade-notice">
          <p class="parade-headline">This year's festival falls on St. Patrick's Day Parade day!</p>
          <p class="parade-text">The parade runs through downtown that morning, so getting there takes a little planning. We've put together everything you need to knowâ€”hotels, light rail, rideshare, and parking options.</p>
          <a href="/travel/" class="travel-link">
            Travel & Parking Guide
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="arrow-icon">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .map-container {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .next-year-teaser {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .next-year-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-shadow: none;
  }
  
  .next-year-description {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .venue-highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 800;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  .venue-highlight::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -2px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .map-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .map-image-container {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .map-image-container:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
  
  .venue-map {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
    transform: scale(1.25);
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  .map-info {
    background-color: transparent;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    box-shadow: none;
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: none;
  }

  .venue-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
    text-shadow: none;
  }
  
  .venue-address {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .venue-location {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-offset);
  }
  
  .venue-description {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.2);
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
  }
  
  .venue-description p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .parade-notice {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.15) 0%, rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.08) 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .parade-headline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .parade-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .travel-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(215, 155, 88, 0.3);
  }

  .travel-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(43, 34, 68, 0.3);
    color: white;
  }

  .arrow-icon {
    width: 1.25rem;
    height: 1.25rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .travel-link:hover .arrow-icon {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .map-content {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .map-image-container {
      flex: 1.3;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .map-info {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    
    .venue-map {
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transform: scale(1.25);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .next-year-title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
    
    .next-year-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .map-info {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
